      "text": [
        ": \"لاَ يَتَزَوَّجِ اَلْأَعْرَابِيُّ اَلْمُهَاجِرَةَ فَيُخْرِجَهَا مِنْ دَارِ اَلْهِجْرَةِ إِلَى اَلْأَعْرَابِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4479 - Imam Abu Ja'far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"An Arab man should not marry a Muhajira woman (a woman who migrated for the sake of faith) and then take her out of the land of migration to the land of the Arabs.\""
        ]
